class Solution {
public:
    bool isMatch(const char *s, const char *p) {
        // Start typing your C/C++ solution below
        // DO NOT write int main() function
        
        
        bool allStar = true;
        int m = 0;
        int n = 0;
        
        while(s[m] != 0){
            m++;
        }
        while(p[n] != 0){
            if(p[n] != '*'){
                allStar = false;
            }
            n++;
        }
  
        if(n == 0){
            return m == 0;
        }else if (m == 0){
            return allStar;
        }
        

        bool table[2][n+1];
        
        table[1][n] = true;
        table[0][n] = false;
  
        for(int j = n-1; j >= 0 ; j--){
            table[1][j] = (p[j] == '*')?table[1][j+1]:false;
        }
        
        for(int i = m-1; i >= 0; i--){
            char c = s[i];
            for(int j = n-1; j >= 0; j--){
                
                switch(p[j]){
                    case '*':
                        table[0][j] = table[1][j] || table[0][j+1];
                        break;
                    case '?':
                        table[0][j] = table[1][j+1];
                        break;
                    default:
                        table[0][j] = (p[j] == c) && table[1][j+1];
                        break;       
                }
            }
            
            for(int j = n; j >= 0; j--){
                table[1][j] = table[0][j];
            }
        }
        return table[0][0];
        
        /*if (*p == 0){
            return (*s == 0);
        }else if (*p == '*'){

                p++;
            }

            //    while( *s != 0 && *s != *(p+1)){
            //        s++;

            //}
            
            return isMatch(s+1,p) || isMatch(s, p+1);
            
        }else if( *p == *s || (*p == '?' && *s != 0)){
            return isMatch(s+1, p+1);
        }
        return false;*/
        
    }
};
